OL,3,CSam Fender 'heartbroken' as he cancels
OL,4,CNewcastle and Glasgow dates
OL,6,FSam Fender has cancelled this month's
OL,7,Fdates in Newcastle and Glasgow.
OL,9,FThe North Shields singer songwriter
OL,10,Fposted on social media on Tuesday
OL,11,Fafternoon (17 December) to say he was
OL,12,F"heartbroken" by the decision which
OL,13,Fwas made due to issues with his vocal
OL,14,Fchords.
OL,16,FHe was due to play to fans in Glasgow
OL,17,Ffor a second night tonight, returning
OL,18,Fto a home crowd on Friday at
OL,19,FNewcastle's Utilita Arena.
