OL,3,CSam Fender 'heartbroken' as he cancels
OL,4,CNewcastle and Glasgow dates
OL,6,FIn a statement posted on X, Fender
OL,7,Fsaid he had had the flu in recent days
OL,8,Fbut had been told by medical
OL,9,Fprofessionals today that he would risk
OL,10,Flasting damage to his voice by
OL,11,Fcontinuing to perform.
OL,13,FHe wrote: "Today I've had an ENT
OL,14,Fscope, camera down my throat and sadly
OL,15,FI've haemorrhaged my right vocal cord,
OL,16,FI'm absolutely heartbroken.
OL,18,F"This has been the best tour so far
OL,19,Fand all I want to do is get up and
OL,20,Fsing again for you all tonight.
