OL,3,CSam Fender 'heartbroken' as he cancels
OL,4,CNewcastle and Glasgow dates
OL,6,F"I've had two separate ENT doctors say
OL,7,Fif I perform tonight I'm risking
OL,8,Flasting damage to my voice and I have
OL,9,Fbeen advised to be on vocal rest and
OL,10,Fnot use my voice for a prolonged
OL,11,Flength of time until it heals."
OL,13,FLast month the award-winning musician
OL,14,Fannounced two more Newcastle gigs at
OL,15,FSt James' Park in 2025.
